------------------------------------------------------------
EN — Material Theme License Agreement
------------------------------------------------------------

1. License to Use
   This agreement grants the user a non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to install and use the "Material Theme" extension on unlimited devices for personal or business purposes. The user is not authorized to modify, distribute, resell, or rent the extension without the written consent of the author.

2. Restrictions
   The user may not:
   a) Reverse engineer, modify, decompile, or disassemble the extension's source code.
   b) Use the extension for illegal or unauthorized activities.
   c) Share the extension through channels other than the official sales channel.

3. Term of Validity
   The license is valid until revoked by Mattia Astorino or the user. Mattia Astorino reserves the right to revoke the license in case of violation of the terms.

4. Intellectual Property
   Mattia Astorino holds all rights, titles, and interests related to the extension, including but not limited to copyright, patents, trademarks, and trade secrets.

5. Limitation of Liability
   The extension is provided "as is," without warranties of any kind. Mattia Astorino shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of the extension.

6. Updates and Support
   Mattia Astorino is not obligated to provide updates or support for the extension. Updates, if available, may be provided for a fee.

7. Acceptance
   By installing and using the extension, the user agrees to the terms and conditions of this license agreement.

